GetOldRoadColors
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

.. code-block:: pascal

    function GetOldRoadColors: Boolean;

Checks if RoadColor matches with any color stored in RoadColors array.
If successful, it sets the roadcolor.

.. note::

    by Wizzup? / WT-Fakawi, edited by EvilChicken!

Example:

